av&eacute;gett, hogy a be&eacute;p&iacute;t&eacute;sre nem ker&uuml;l&otilde;
&eacute;p&iacute;t&otilde;anyagok &eacute;s fogy&oacute;eszk&ouml;z&ouml;k
a v&aacute;mhat&oacute;s&aacute;gok &aacute;ltal meghat&aacute;rozott id&otilde;pontban
