<br>3. A Felek k&ouml;lcs&ouml;n&ouml;sen biztos&iacute;tj&aacute;k az
illet&eacute;kmentesen &aacute;tsz&aacute;ll&iacute;t&aacute;sra ker&uuml;l&otilde;
&eacute;p&iacute;t&otilde;anyagok, fogy&oacute;eszk&ouml;z&ouml;k, g&eacute;pek
